                    <button class="btn btn-link p-0 text-muted-light shadow-none text-decoration-none"><span class="material-symbols-outlined fs-5">more_horiz</span></button>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-display fw-semibold fs-6 mb-1 text-truncate text-dark">Q3 Brand Campaign Launch</h3>
                <p class="small text-muted-light mb-auto" style="display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden;">Finalizing assets and media buying for the upcoming quarter.</p>
                
